   In expected or unexpected moments, HSBC’s experts are there to advise
   you.
   Real estate purchases
   Other projects
   [tile-construire-patrimoine-premier-hsbc-france.jpg]

Grow your assets


   Free access to our experts who will help you prepare for the future.
   Preferential rates
   HSBC expertise
   HSBC Premier Privileges
   [tile-partout-avecvous-premier-hsbc-france1.jpg]

By your side wherever you are in the world


   Traveller or expat, take advantage of our dedicated services in every
   HSBC branch.
   Your travels
   Moving countries
   [content-avantages-premier-hsbc-france.jpg]

   As an HSBC Premier customer, you could, for example, save €231 in
   advantages.

   Example 1

   A couple with three children could save €231 on standard HSBC fees^(2):
     * Waiver of current account fees on a joint account: €24
     * Providing 2 free Electron debit cards: €70
     * Free annual wealth report: €22
     * No fees for a €10,000 new baby personal loan: €100 (estimate)
     * International emergency cash: €15 (one emergency encashment per
       year)

   Get a 50% discount on the providing of a second debit card for the same
   account^(3)

   Example 2

   A customer moving to the UK could save €311 on standard HSBC fees^(3):
     * Waiver of current account fees: €24
     * Free account opening service in the UK: €140
     * Global View/Global Transfer services: €125 (calculated on the basis
       of 10 transfers per year)
     * Free annual wealth report: €22
       []

   Open an account Open an account for HSBC Premier

HSBC Premier in summary

    1. The support of a dedicated HSBC Premier advisor
    2. No maintenance fees for current accounts
    3. Dedicated real estate purchasing service and funding for your
       projects
    4. Customised support to build you and your family’s legacy
    5. Our best international services are offered to our HSBC Premier
       clients
    6. Exclusive advantages alongside our partners with HSBC Privileges

   Open an account Open an account for HSBC Premier

To take advantage of these benefits, you can:

     * Secure your personal revenues at HSBC France (salary, retirement,
       mortgage) with a minimum amount of € 4,500 per month (or € 6,000
       for a household).
     * Or trust us with at least € 75,000 worth of assets (deposits,
       savings, life insurance, securities).

   (1) Monday to Friday from 08:00 am to 10:00 pm. Saturday from 09:00 am
   to 05:30 pm. For public holidays, opening hours are from 09:00 am to
   05:30 pm. Unless a contrary indication is mentioned, public holidays on
   weekdays (Monday to Saturday) are business days, except May 1^st and
   December 25th.

   (2) Discounts calculated on the basis of the HSBC France price list
   applicable on 1st October 2018.

   (3) Discount applied to all HSBC France customers for providing any
   identical personal debit or lower category card on the same account.

